PrecisAmendments to the IMMIGRATION REGULATIONS, 1978 which exempt elementary and secondary school age dependents of duly authorized foreign workers or students from the requirements of proof of enrolment and proof of sufficient financial means, and will allow foreign students to accept a job on the campus of the post-secondary institution they are attending.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1995-0353 Publication Date: 1995-08-09
Attachments
precis:
Amendments to the IMMIGRATION REGULATIONS, 1978 which exempt elementary and
secondary school age dependents of duly authorized foreign workers or
students from the requirements of proof of enrolment and proof of
sufficient financial means, and will allow foreign students to accept a job
on the campus of the post-secondary institution they are attending.
